# libiqxmlrpc - High-Performance Fork

This is a performance-focused fork of Anton Dedov's libiqxmlrpc, actively maintained and enhanced since 2019.

## Why This Fork?

âš¡ **28 performance optimizations** delivering 1.2x to 12.5x speedups on critical operations
ðŸš€ **Modern C++17** with `string_view`, `to_chars`, and safe integer operations
ðŸ”’ **Enhanced security** with TLS 1.2+, overflow protection, and fuzzing infrastructure
ðŸ“¦ **Drop-in compatible** with upstream for most use cases (see Doxygen `\note` tags for breaking changes since 0.14.0)

## Quick Start

```bash
# Ubuntu/Debian
sudo apt install libboost-dev libxml2-dev libssl-dev cmake g++

# Clone and build
git clone https://github.com/yarikmsu/libiqxmlrpc.git
cd libiqxmlrpc
cmake -S . -B build -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release
cmake --build build
sudo cmake --install build
```

**See the [5-minute Quick Start guide](https://github.com/yarikmsu/libiqxmlrpc/wiki/Quick-Start) for complete instructions.**

