## Performance Highlights

| Optimization | Speedup | Impact |
|--------------|---------|--------|
| Number conversion | 12.5x | High - affects all numeric values |
| Type checking | 10.5x | High - frequently used operations |
| HTTP parsing | 3.3x | Medium - one-time per request |
| SSL exceptions | 850x | Low - error paths only |

**See [Performance Results](https://github.com/yarikmsu/libiqxmlrpc/wiki/Performance-Results) for complete benchmark data.**

## Requirements

- **Compiler**: GCC 7+ or Clang 5+ (C++17 support)
- **CMake**: 3.10+
- **Dependencies**: Boost 1.58+, libxml2 2.9+, OpenSSL 1.1.0+

